{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究电荷能否在导体中运动；知道电流的本质。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种电荷相互排斥，异种电荷相互吸引。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">橡胶棒、带绝缘柄的金属棒、验电器、带电小球</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.用带电小球接触一个验电器顶端，使验电器带上电；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.用橡胶棒把两个验电器顶端相连起来，观察两个验电器张角的变化；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.用带有绝缘柄的金属棒把两个验电器连接起来，观察两个验电器张角的变化。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有一部分电荷通过金属棒从一个验电器移动到了另一个验电器，电荷发生了定向移动。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正电荷定向移动的方向规定为电流的方向；负电荷定向移动方向与电流方向相反。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}